subject: Automobile Racing
Accidents and Safety
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick’s first career Nascar race ended with a jolt of reality when she finished 35th among 43 drivers after being caught in a 12-car wreck.
